#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:2
msgid "检测工具参考"
msgstr "Inspection Tool Reference"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:4
msgid "本章逐一介绍每种 2D 检测工具的参数与配置方法。每个工具单独成页。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter walks through the parameters and configuration of each 2D "
"inspection tool, one page per tool."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:6
msgid ""
"本章节详细介绍 2D 检测工具（检测项）及其参数含义。每个元件可包含一个或多个检测项；在 **模板编辑器** "
"中选中元件后，可在右侧面板查看并编辑各检测项的参数。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter documents each 2D inspection tool (also called an *inspection "
"item*) and the meaning of its parameters. A component can carry one or more "
"inspection items; selecting the component in the **Template Editor** exposes"
" their parameters in the right-hand panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:-1
msgid "检测参数总览"
msgstr "Inspection parameters overview"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:12
msgid "在阅读各工具参数前，先了解几个贯穿全篇的通用概念："
msgstr ""
"Before reading the per-tool parameter pages, get familiar with a few "
"concepts that recur throughout:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:14
msgid ""
"**AI 异常分数**：基于 AI 模型的检测会输出一个 0~1 的异常分数；接近 0 表示与正常样本相似，接近 1 表示差异大。可通过统计图表对比正常"
" / 异常样本的分数分布，选择合适的判定阈值。"
msgstr ""
"**AI anomaly score**: AI-driven inspections output an anomaly score between "
"0 and 1; values near 0 indicate the sample looks normal, values near 1 "
"indicate a large deviation. Use the score-distribution histograms to compare"
" OK vs. NG samples and pick a sensible threshold."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:15
msgid ""
"**颜色范围与有效比例（Valid Ratio）**：基于颜色的检测在 ROI 内用 **HSV 颜色范围** "
"将像素二值化为\"有效点\"，有效比例定义为 :math:`100 \\times \\dfrac{\\text{有效点数}}{\\text{ROI "
"面积}}`。判定时检查有效比例是否落入设定的 **有效比例范围**。一个 ROI 可配置多组颜色范围，分别独立判定。"
msgstr ""
"**Color range and Valid Ratio**: color-based inspections binarize pixels "
"inside the ROI using an **HSV color range**; pixels passing the range are "
"counted as *valid pixels*, and the valid ratio is defined as :math:`100 "
"\\times \\dfrac{\\text{valid pixel count}}{\\text{ROI area}}`. The decision "
"checks whether the valid ratio falls inside the configured **Valid Ratio "
"Range**. A single ROI can be configured with multiple color ranges, each "
"evaluated independently."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:16
msgid ""
"**颜色公式（Color Formula）**：定义如何从像素计算颜色特征。可选 HSV（中心 / 起止色调 + "
"明度范围），或三色公式（Tricolor，如 ``2B-R-G`` 线性组合，配合 X/Y/Z/A 系数与阈值）。"
msgstr ""
"**Color Formula**: defines how the color feature is computed from each "
"pixel. Choose **HSV** (center hue plus start/end hue, with a value range), "
"or a **Tricolor** formula such as ``2B-R-G`` (a linear combination "
"configured with X / Y / Z / A coefficients and a threshold)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:17
msgid "**对齐（Alignment）**：部分检测在判定前先将元件图像与标准样本自动对齐，以消除位置偏移带来的误判。"
msgstr ""
"**Alignment**: some inspections automatically register the inspected "
"component image against the golden reference before deciding, eliminating "
"false positives caused by positional shift."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:18
msgid ""
"**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：评估后叠加显示二值化 / "
"检测中间结果，便于调参；因有额外计算开销，建议仅在调试阶段开启。"
msgstr ""
"**Enable Visualization**: after an evaluation run, overlays the binarized "
"mask and intermediate detection results to help with tuning. Carries extra "
"compute cost, so enable only while debugging."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/index.rst:19
msgid ""
"**使用共享参数（Use Shared Parameters）**：元件加入封装 / "
"料号分组后默认与组内共享参数；关闭后可对该实例单独调参，不再继承分组设置。"
msgstr ""
"**Use Shared Parameters**: once a component is placed in a package or part-"
"number group, it shares parameters with the group by default. Turn the "
"switch off to tune this specific instance independently — the component no "
"longer inherits the group's settings."
